nodes.text: Star Wars: Doctor Aphra Vol. 7 — A Rogue's End

Star Wars: Doctor Aphra Vol. 7 — A Rogue's End is a canon trade paperback that collects issues 37–40 of the comic-book series Star Wars: Doctor Aphra and Doctor Aphra Annual 3 from author Simon Spurrier. It was published by Marvel Comics on February 11, 2020.

After all she's been through, professional disaster zone DOCTOR APHRA is right back where she started: working for DARTH VADER. What villainous use has the dark lord found for her to make him spare the life of his most annoying foe…? And how long does she have to try to slither out of harm's way before he decides to finish what he started three years ago…?
COLLECTING: Doctor Aphra (2016) 37-40, Star Wars: Doctor Aphra Annual (2016) 3, material from Star Wars: Empire Ascendant (2019) 1
